  <summary date="2021-09-13T16:51:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Smoke-Free Schools Act of 2019

This bill prohibits the use of any tobacco product (e.g., electronic nicotine delivery systems such as e-cigarettes) in an indoor facility that is regularly used for children's services, including health care, day care, early development, education, or library services. Current law prohibits smoking in such facilities.</summary>
